Summary: Object with 3 yellow lights over Horseneck beach
trends: There have been 3 other sightings in Westport
There were no other sightings in Westport on or around July 30th 2009
divs: Sighting DetailsI was at John Reed Rd going to Gumbys Head when I saw this really bright object. At first, I was thinking it was a star because it was not moving, but I noticed that this was 3 lights together. I could see for approximately 5 minutes, then it simply disappeared without movement or sound. It was not an airplane. I can say because I worked 5 years in a airport when I was in the Air Force.
